Ohio Promise Award — Alexa Russell, $2,000; Baylee Tracy, $2,000; Marissa Allen, $2,000; Hannah Durst, $2,000; Shelby Whaley, $2,000; Breanna Lilly, $2,000; Madeline Shope, $2,000;

